channel.title: My voule autorestarter won't work! picture inside!
channel.description:

[IMG]http://i195.photobucket.com/albums/z82/musicmad441/ownage1.jpg[/img]
Then when I try and log in with kewl.no-ip.info, it says this:
[IMG]http://i195.photobucket.com/albums/z82/musicmad441/ownage2.jpg[/img]
and btw, kewl.no-ip.info is my server, so what is my problem?
Many Thanks
Music
